    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## TASK__Escalate\nHourly escalation workflow.\n\n- Finds open tasks overdue by more than 24 hours\n- Marks each task escalated and upgrades priority to critical\n- Notifies the assignee's manager when manager_slack_id exists\n- Alerts #ops-alerts for every escalation\n- Writes one audit log entry per run",
        "height": 420,
